WEBVTT

00:00:08.241 --> 00:00:09.576
My name is Rebecca Rudderham.

00:00:09.576 --> 00:00:12.112
I am the principal at Fundy Middle
and High School.

00:00:12.112 --> 00:00:15.882
So PLCs professional learning communities
at Fundy Middle and High School.

00:00:15.882 --> 00:00:19.686
The we have structured it
in such a way that they are

00:00:19.686 --> 00:00:23.256
schedule staff are scheduled to meet twice
every month.

00:00:23.656 --> 00:00:28.762
And during these scheduled times they
our staff discuss the school improvement

00:00:28.762 --> 00:00:32.298
plan initiatives that they want
to move forward with, or they will discuss

00:00:32.565 --> 00:00:37.370
content based,
planning for for our school.

00:00:37.370 --> 00:00:40.974
So it entails these structured,

00:00:41.274 --> 00:00:44.911
meeting times in place
as well as they meet all the time.

00:00:44.911 --> 00:00:49.382
And the staff rooms, lots of informal
conversations about student learning,

00:00:49.382 --> 00:00:53.053
lots of excitement about upcoming plans
and improvement for our school.

00:00:53.553 --> 00:00:57.090
I think it's extremely
important that, that

00:00:58.625 --> 00:00:59.592
the, the roll

00:00:59.592 --> 00:01:04.297
out of it is, done
in such a way that you, you get staff

00:01:04.297 --> 00:01:08.234
Buy-In and they recognize the importance
of working as a team.

00:01:08.234 --> 00:01:11.237
And I think that's
what's the most exciting part about,

00:01:11.371 --> 00:01:14.474
the initiative that we're involved in
right now with the middle school pilot

00:01:14.474 --> 00:01:19.012
is that with through the math momentum,
our, our teams, have

00:01:20.046 --> 00:01:23.383
gathered together,
they have seen the what what working

00:01:23.383 --> 00:01:27.620
as a group can actually do it
and how it how it, eases

00:01:27.887 --> 00:01:32.625
the planning phase, how you can actually,
gauge the achievement of the kids.

00:01:32.625 --> 00:01:33.626
You can see the data

00:01:33.626 --> 00:01:37.464
that the kids are engaged and they're
excited about learning new concepts.

00:01:37.697 --> 00:01:43.536
So this particular, initiative
has allowed us to get some more buy in.

00:01:43.536 --> 00:01:47.273
And the staff does seem to be really,
really excited about working together

00:01:47.273 --> 00:01:50.243
