00:01:50.643 --> 00:01:53.246
how how it can make planning easier.

00:01:53.246 --> 00:01:54.948
We've really kind of,

00:01:55.949 --> 00:01:57.083
opted to go in this direction

00:01:57.083 --> 00:02:00.753
because we recognize
that we were meeting as teams.

